Title: Valor ceramic coal set
Description: This Valor 5115227 ceramic coal set is compatible with selected appliances. These fire coals are used only in appliances with no closed burner, allowing heat to be circulated. Manufactured to fit together in a specific way, these coals ensure complete combustion and if not correctly assembled harmful gases can escape. Please read instructions carefully or call a registered gas safe engineer.
